data.description: Back on the market not the fault of the Seller. Beautiful Home in the sought after River Ridge swim and tennis community! This 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home has many upgrades and nice light fixtures. The downstairs has a semi-open floor plan into the large den from the kitchen area and is great for entertainment. Guest Bedroom and full bath on the main floor. The kitchen has beautiful granite counters. There are 4 spacious additional rooms upstairs including the Master suite that boasts an oversized room along with a tray ceiling. The bathroom has both a tub and shower and has double sinks. Property is located close to the Georgia International Horse Park and I-20 along with local shopping and restaurants. The seller is the Agent.
